Week 2: Core Machine Learning Algorithms
📋 Learning Objectives
By the end of this week, you will be able to:

✅ Understand the difference between supervised and unsupervised learning

✅ Implement Linear Regression for prediction tasks

✅ Use Logistic Regression for binary classification

✅ Apply K-Nearest Neighbors for both regression and classification

✅ Split data into training and testing sets

✅ Evaluate models using appropriate metrics

✅ Avoid overfitting and underfitting

✅ Build and compare multiple models on real datasets

